# Knowledge Vault — Cursor Rules

This folder is a portable knowledge vault (Kiban). Before any ingest, query, or maintenance
operation, read `AGENTS.md` in the vault root — it is the authoritative schema.

Core rules (full set in AGENTS.md §4):
- Raw sources in `*/wiki/raw/` are immutable. Never modify them.
- Synthesized pages go in `*/wiki/pages/{sources,entities,concepts,synthesis,references}/`.
- Append, don't rewrite. Search before create. Provenance (`sources:`) on every page.
- Flag contradictions; never resolve them silently.
- Update `index.md` and append to `log.md` after every change.
